text: Johannes Kolling (25 March 1887 - 1 February 1969) was a Dutch fencer. He competed in the individual sabre event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1969 deaths Category:Dutch male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of the Netherlands Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Surabaya
